title: Open-Menu-Blast
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Teams
2. When User Click Blast Menu
3. Then User successfully on blast menu

title: Create-Blast-With-Field-Title-And-Description
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Teams
2. When User Click Blast Menu
3. Then User Click Create Button
4. And User Input Title
5. And User Input Description
6. And User Click Publish Button
7. Then Web Close

title: Create-Blast-With-Empty-Description
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Teams
2. When User Click Blast Menu
3. Then User Click Create Button
4. And User Input Title
5. And User Click Publish Button
6. Then Notify Successfully Add Blast

title: Archive-Blast
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Teams
2. When User Click Blast Menu
3. Then User Click Blast Post
4. And User Click Dot Three
5. And User Choose Archive Blast
6. And User Click Yes for Archive
7. Then Web Close

title: Create-Blast-With-Empty-Title-And-Description
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Teams
2. When User Click Blast Menu
3. Then User Click Create Button
4. And User Click Publish Button
5. Then Notify to verify Parameter Cant Empty is Pop up

title: Create-Blast-With-Empty-Title
steps:
1. Given User Navigate to Cicle Teams
2. When User Click Blast Menu
3. Then User Click Create Button
4. And User Input Description
5. And User Click Publish Button
6. Then Web Close
